Package projecttwo

Class EnrollStudent

  • java.lang.Object
    • projecttwo.EnrollStudent
  • public class EnrollStudent
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a student that is enrolled, and must be in the roster. These students have a profile and a number of credits completed prior to being enrolled.
    Author:
    Aryan Jairath, Anis Chihoub
